    "b, Human-human interaction.",
    "This is conceptually similar to the human-AI interaction, except the AI (level 2) is replaced with human participants.",
    "The participants in level 2 are presented with the arrays and responses of the participants in level 1 (training phase) and then judge new arrays on their own as either more sad or more happy (test phase).",
    "The participants in level 3 are then presented with the responses of the human participants from level 2 and asked whether they would like to change their initial response.",
    "c, Human-AI-perceivedas-human interaction."
